  <!-- EN: Thunder minigun【First-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_ThunderMinigun.label>雷霆连珠铳【一品】</RI_Weapon_ThunderMinigun.label>
  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Range weapon\n\nA beaded machine gun, capable of attracting the force of angry thunder, fired a bullet with a weak electric charge, enough to tear through heavy armor. After loading the spiritual crystal, it can also shoot powerful lightning. -->
  <RI_Weapon_ThunderMinigun.description>【一品】远程兵器\n\n一挺可以引来怒雷之力的连珠机枪，射出的子弹附带有微弱的电力，足以撕开厚重的装甲。在装填灵石后，还能射出威力强大的雷电。</RI_Weapon_ThunderMinigun.description>
  <!-- EN: ThunderMinigun -->
  <RI_Weapon_ThunderMinigun.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>闷雷穿云</RI_Weapon_ThunderMinigun.comps.CompEquippableAbilityReloadable.chargeNoun>
  <!-- EN: on cooldown -->
