  <!-- EN: 【First-rate】Range weapon\n\nA longbow made from the spirit of sky and earth, using a thrumbo horn and mechanical structure as the bow body, each arrow carries a low temperature, which can gradually freeze the enemy. -->
  <RI_Weapon_WhiteApeBow.description>【一品】远程兵器\n\n一把集天地灵气而成的长弓，使用了敲击兽角和机械结构作为弓身，每一箭都附带低温，可以逐渐冻结敌人。</RI_Weapon_WhiteApeBow.description>
